     aspirations.  Sentient worms implanted into victims\' spinal cords.  
     Grav cavalry combat.  Noble classes. Hookers.  Kusari-jitsu.  Schrager 
     Mk-I SCrew -fu.  Learned quotations -fu. Lotsa skin-tight spacesuits, 
     lots more dead bodies.  Sudet-Bob says check it out."
     
