     feeling make it worth your dollar.  Future Shadow Empires stories are 
     likely to follow.
     
     Dark Horse Comics usually reprints all their miniseries into trade 
     paperbacks at some point.  The price might range from between $9.95 
     and $14.95, but I can get them for 35% off with no tax (don\'tcha love 
     mail order?! <g>).  If any of you are interested in this series, let 
     me know and I\'ll notify you if and when the TPB gets printed.  
     Otherwise, I\'m sure you can find copies of the actual 4-issue 
     miniseries at your local comics shop.  
     
     In addition, if any of you want to get it for cheap, I\'ll repost this 
