all your designs have no EMM, they cannot even be justified as being
stealthy, 
and they only serve to complicate maintenance - Max I would like your (plus
any 
other XBoaters) opinions

CSV - Combat Support vehicle (modern day equivalent: various vehicles based
on 
MBT chassis).  Nice one Max - you have a handle on combat support and those 
other jolly force multipliers most folk forget...

MGB - Meson Gun Boat
 
DESIGN VARIATIONS

MBGT - 10 Ton vehicle, 72G Armour, Main Gun FZ14, RPA14 * 2 point defence
guns.
