Jeffrey is questioning the role of the RCEV vehicle. In my view this was 
actually covering three different roles:

Commo Veh. using two drones yet to be designed. Since commo will mostly be
via direct lineof sight beams, efficient commo in broken terrain etc requires
relay stations. These are provided by the drones deployed by this vechile.

Reco Veh. theidea is to use the drone for reco missions that might 
