      _/ Sr. Unix Specialist   UUCP: ..!uunet!tcgny!berghold          _/
     _/VOX: (718) 355-2722 INTERNET: peterb@cnct.com                 _/
    _/ FAX: (718) 355-4734      URL: http://cnct.com/~peterb        _/
