    'index' => 'ab519',
    'month' => '06',
    'body' => 'I\'ve always treated it as something like #3 (although I based mine on the
invisibility spells in Randal Garrett\'s Lord Darcy series).  You may hear
something, but you can\'t pin it down (ie. can\'t get a sensor lock).  By
concentrating really hard (Formidable and Impossible Observation, with
Willpower as enabling characteristic) you might be able to deduce the area
where your eyes don\'t focus.  (Then, of course, you can use area fire against
it, or whip out a camera and get evidence, or whatever.)
