10/8-95 Cmdr. Lilly <a.s.lilly@bnr.co.uk> wrote:

>I found this interesting in that a number of previous posts
>have said that canon required jumps to be to/from certain
>gravity densities, i.e. Jump 1 could only jump to the largest
>gravity well within a system, Jump 2 could choose that or
>the next largest gravity well, etc.
>
