of checking: those that are commonly available on Earth today. Unfortunately
I have no ready reference material. Could some kind soul, who knows about
weapon prices, let me know the prices of revolvers, automatics, shotguns,
rifles, SMGs, etc.? Also, the value of a dollar today (compared to the
dollar in 1977, where one Credit was roughly equivalent to a dollar).


