Border Worlds and all but five of the Sword Worlds (and, unrelatedly,
the entire Islands Cluster) have been annexed by the Regency. The
remaining rump state agitates for liberation of the "occupied systems"
from the "Imperials" (sic), and some in said systems heed this
call. The exact reason for the annexation eludes me right now, but I
think it was some kind of "security" matter (but aren\'t all
annexations that way?).  Significant numbers of refugees were settled
in that region after they fled the trailing Deneb sector area during
the Virus outbreak, and their second- and third-generation descendants
now live along side the original Sword Worlders\' descendants, creating
a bit of tension.

