Players\' Manual with me right now. In my edition of the PM
(it\'s a newer edition, as the first one I had was worn out),
there are two alternate rules for hand to hand combat. One
rule is the original, where you first determine if an attack can
be made, and then determine if you acually hit. As far as I
remember, STR is a modifier to the first task (but I may very
well be wrong).

