aforementioned ones. It is a confrontation task, and I _think_
I remember, that STR is a DM there (some of my players
have just got themselves some bionics - as detailed in TD
13 - with STR 40, and are very enthusiastic about how
awesome they would be in a brawl - they should maybe
have thought about all the social drawbacks I intend to
throw in their faces - but I digress...). Maybe someone on
this list with access to a newer edition of PM could check
this out.

