proofreading error, but what about a blockade requiring
"several" of the "largest line-of-battle vessel[s]
currently in service with the Imperial Navy in the
Spinward Marches"?  

Is the Imperium trying to keep something from getting out
of Andor and Candory, or trying to keep someone from
getting in?  Or is it really just a cover or excuse for
building up Imperial forces on the opposite side of the
Sword Worlds? 

Does anyone recall seeing anything else about a 
heavily-enforced "blockade" of Andor and Candory in any 
other materials?  (I didn\'t see anything in the Droyne Alien 
Supplement, nor in Alien Realms.)

And, of course, I solicit your thoughts on the Thyo Supud
in light of the foregoing.

