>if the _Regency Sourcebook_ gives us much of an update on the races in the
>Spinward Marches (Vargr, Zhodani, Droyne, LOTS o\'minor races)?

More "en-passant" references than huge slabs, although the Sword Worlders and
Darrians get about a page each (as do the New/Old Islands). The Zhos do get a
large mention, although (as a list member said) more along the "destroyed alien
of the month club"-type line, than a real write-up. The Vargr seem to be i/c
most organised Regency criminal activity (although who ran it before??). The
Droyne are almost not mentioned at all, although if you have been following
the traveller list you would have seen the HUGE discussion on Candory and
Andor, still interdicted but now at TL 13-14 with B (?) class \'ports.

- Hyphen
